text: Story of the hard working girl who paid for items she never received. My package from @Forever21 was never delivered by @FedEx - repeatedly called fedex who told me it was deemed lost each time. F21 repeatedly told me in their system, fedex deemed it delivered. No refund/credit.
@kelseashells Hello, this is Andrew. We apologize for this issue. Please DM @FedExHelp your name, delivery address, tracking & phone numbers and I would be happy to research this for you.
@FedExHelp Great, I dm-ed you. When researched, you’ll find that you deemed it lost or stolen. Just refused to provide me with written confirmation.

@FedExHelp @FedEx: by “delivering” we just mean that our drivers scan it as delivered so now it’s your problem 🤷🏻‍♀️ 

...also, we can’t give you any written proof of what we confirm over the phone 👍🏼 https://t.co/soaQT7HO5p
